An addendum to http://thepiratebay.se/torrent/6501757/The_Shadow_(200__episodes)_-_updated

20 additional episodes not included in the above torrent--from several seasons, including the Australian series, some fragments and incomplete episodes.  

Please read the note about file names and duplicate titles.  I have tried to keep this archive organized, but there are a lot of files and there is some confusion about the way certain episodes are named and/or dated.

You will also find a list of episodes which are believed to exist, but which I do not have.  If you can offer a factual correction, a missing episode, insight or really any information regarding these, please contact me.

I am working to organize a complete master torrent for everything The Shadow.  This includes the radio shows, comics books (from DC to Dynamite), 330+ pulp novels, films (including the rare 15-part serial films), history, art and even Nintendo game ROMs.  It will be some time before I can complete this archive.

Any help to this effect would be greatly appreciated.

